Something feels off here.

148
00:15:19,126 --> 00:15:20,210
Did something happen?

149
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,506
Try some.

150
00:15:24,590 --> 00:15:27,176
The restaurant lady packed this for you.

151
00:15:28,302 --> 00:15:29,678
Something is definitely off.

152
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:31,096
