Sorry. It's me.

195
00:20:06,371 --> 00:20:07,706
You haven't found her yet?

196
00:20:08,707 --> 00:20:11,126
I searched everywhere,
but I didn't see her.

197
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:14,087
You should stay here
and call me if Ms. Hong comes back.

198
00:20:14,171 --> 00:20:15,339
Okay.

199
00:20:17,966 --> 00:20:19,593
Where are you going?

200
00:20:19,676 --> 00:20:21,386
