to the kid she tried to kill.

211
00:21:22,656 --> 00:21:25,701
In-beom…

212
00:21:27,786 --> 00:21:31,832
It's all my fault.

213
00:21:35,544 --> 00:21:38,422
You can't die, In-beom.

214
00:21:39,798 --> 00:21:41,174
Mr. Oh.

215
00:21:48,515 --> 00:21:51,184
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

216
00:21:51,268 --> 00:21:55,480
He said he would give me
an apartment unit in return.

217
00:21:56,273 --> 00:22:00,444
I must have gone mad. I'm so sorry.

218
00:22:00,527 --> 00:22:03,447
So it is you that created the egg ghost.

219
00:22:04,448 --> 00:22:08,076
The spirits of the seven people who died
in a fire you set became an egg ghost.

220
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:10,078
And Mi-jin died trying to exorcise it.

221
00:22:10,162 --> 00:22:12,622
