Put this necklace on your nephew.

229
00:22:39,858 --> 00:22:42,402
As long as he's wearing it,
it'll never happen.

230
00:22:43,361 --> 00:22:46,823
Make sure he never takes it off,
no matter what.

231
00:22:47,532 --> 00:22:49,576
Okay. Thank you.

232
00:22:49,659 --> 00:22:50,911
