249
00:24:02,065 --> 00:24:03,984
You betrayed

250
00:24:04,818 --> 00:24:06,319
her only trust.

251
00:24:12,826 --> 00:24:13,994
Thank you very much

252
00:24:15,954 --> 00:24:17,205
for this necklace.

253
00:24:18,582 --> 00:24:22,210
