269
00:26:28,169 --> 00:26:29,629
I sold the realty office too.

270
00:26:34,634 --> 00:26:36,219
You must mean it this time.

271
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,471
How will you make a living then?

272
00:26:40,015 --> 00:26:41,182
I'm going to travel.

273
00:26:41,266 --> 00:26:43,601
Travel, my foot. You're a homebody.

274
00:26:43,685 --> 00:26:44,811
You hate traveling.

275
00:26:45,395 --> 00:26:47,647
I can't stay home forever.

276
00:26:50,650 --> 00:26:52,485
I don't think you'll be able to quit.

277
00:26:53,862 --> 00:26:55,030
I can.

278
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:58,033
Do you really think
you've been doing this job

279
00:26:58,116 --> 00:27:01,328
because you haven't been able
to put your mother to rest?

280
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:05,582
You say you're sick of them
and never want to see them again,

281
00:27:05,665 --> 00:27:07,542
but I doubt you can turn a blind eye

282
00:27:07,625 --> 00:27:10,503
to vengeful spirits shivering in the cold
and living in pain.

283
00:27:10,587 --> 00:27:12,005
That was my mom.

284
00:27:12,088 --> 00:27:13,506
And you're just like her.

285
00:27:27,729 --> 00:27:29,397
Don't be so hard on yourself.

286
00:27:30,273 --> 00:27:31,941
She was bound to find out someday.

287
00:27:32,859 --> 00:27:33,985
If possible,

288
00:27:35,987 --> 00:27:37,739
I never wanted her to find out.

289
00:27:41,576 --> 00:27:43,578
Ji-a is a grown-up.

290
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:46,247
She can deal with this on her own.

291
00:27:51,586 --> 00:27:56,424
Detective Kang's been helping me
with re-investigating Do Hak-seong.

292
00:27:57,050 --> 00:27:59,177
When you brokered the sale of Green Villa,

293
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:02,889
someone uploaded the call recording
between Hwang and Do online.

294
00:28:03,556 --> 00:28:04,974
It was you, wasn't it?

295
00:28:05,642 --> 00:28:07,727
Could I listen to the original file?

296
00:28:09,562 --> 00:28:11,189
How can I trust this man?

297
00:28:11,773 --> 00:28:13,316
Someone told me

298
00:28:14,359 --> 00:28:16,111
there's more than meets the eye.

299
00:28:17,445 --> 00:28:18,822
That everything has

300
00:28:19,823 --> 00:28:21,032
its hidden side.

301
00:28:41,094 --> 00:28:42,053
CHANGHWA RESTAURANT

302
00:28:52,772 --> 00:28:54,190
You'll find Ji-a there.

303
00:28:59,028 --> 00:29:01,197
BLUE SALT

304
00:29:31,603 --> 00:29:33,521
Are you the psychic at Daebak Realty?

305
00:29:33,605 --> 00:29:35,190
How did you know?

306
00:29:36,399 --> 00:29:37,692
I made that.

307
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:45,492
Where is Ms. Hong?

308
00:29:46,701 --> 00:29:49,287
I think she just went
into the bamboo forest.

309
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:51,581
Wait inside.
She'll return before the sun sets.

310
00:29:51,664 --> 00:29:53,082
I'll go catch her.

311
00:29:58,004 --> 00:30:00,131
He's as good-looking as she said.

312
00:30:19,609 --> 00:30:21,736
-I need to talk to you.
-I have nothing to say.

313
00:30:22,946 --> 00:30:24,823
But I do, so please listen.

314
00:30:26,741 --> 00:30:28,618
I heard everything from Ms. Joo.

315
00:30:34,791 --> 00:30:36,584
It wasn't your fault.

316
00:30:37,627 --> 00:30:39,087
As you said,

317
00:30:39,170 --> 00:30:43,675
if my uncle and I hadn't come that day,
your mother wouldn't have passed away.

318
00:30:47,595 --> 00:30:49,514
So let's not be sorry.

319
00:30:50,431 --> 00:30:52,183
I'm not going to be sorry

320
00:30:52,267 --> 00:30:54,769
for what happened with my uncle anymore,

321
00:30:54,853 --> 00:30:58,273
so don't be sorry
for what happened with your mother.

322
00:30:59,274 --> 00:31:00,525
After all,

323
00:31:01,234 --> 00:31:02,569
I'm still alive.

324
00:31:05,613 --> 00:31:07,240
But my mother is dead.

325
00:31:13,872 --> 00:31:15,039
I…

326
00:31:17,625 --> 00:31:19,919
I killed my mom with my own hands.

327
00:31:20,628 --> 00:31:22,338
And that's how you're still alive.

328
00:31:23,506 --> 00:31:25,383
Whenever I see you,

329
00:31:27,552 --> 00:31:31,055
I'm vividly reminded
of the fact that I killed my mother.

330
00:31:33,099 --> 00:31:35,101
So I can't see you anymore.

331
00:32:26,903 --> 00:32:28,363
I'm going home.

332
00:32:30,198 --> 00:32:31,783
I know you're not asleep.

333
00:32:32,575 --> 00:32:36,037
I don't expect you to show your face,
but you should at least say bye.

334
00:32:38,164 --> 00:32:39,165
Darn it.

335
00:32:53,304 --> 00:32:56,099
Do you want to know
how to avoid becoming a vengeful spirit?

336
00:32:57,016 --> 00:32:57,850
Sorry?

337
00:32:59,185 --> 00:33:01,521
When you're thankful,
express your gratitude.

338
00:33:02,146 --> 00:33:03,940
When you've done wrong, apologize.

339
00:33:04,023 --> 00:33:06,985
And show affection to those you love.

340
00:33:09,070 --> 00:33:10,571
Who knows when we'll die?

341
00:33:11,197 --> 00:33:13,157
We shouldn't hesitate or be afraid.

342
00:33:13,241 --> 00:33:16,327
What if you die in a car accident today?
Won't you feel bitter?

343
00:33:17,036 --> 00:33:18,997
Say what you want to or must

344
00:33:19,080 --> 00:33:21,499
if you don't want to turn
into a vengeful spirit.

345
00:33:22,542 --> 00:33:25,795
Wait. Or will that prevent
the other person from becoming one?

346
00:33:26,546 --> 00:33:27,797
I don't know.

347
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:31,384
BLUE SALT

348
00:33:53,948 --> 00:33:55,033
It's me.

349
00:33:57,910 --> 00:33:59,245
I came

350
00:34:00,496 --> 00:34:02,582
to tell you something for the last time.

351
00:34:03,833 --> 00:34:05,168
You were the one

352
00:34:06,210 --> 00:34:08,421
who saved me 20 years ago.

353
00:34:09,881 --> 00:34:11,632
Thank you.

354
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:22,018
Also, you were the first person
to tell me that I was special

355
00:34:22,518 --> 00:34:26,314
and that I was a good person.

356
00:34:28,357 --> 00:34:29,734
Thank you for that as well.

357
00:34:34,572 --> 00:34:36,491
Eat your favorite dishes,

358
00:34:36,574 --> 00:34:38,159
watch your favorite shows,

359
00:34:38,826 --> 00:34:40,286
and buy whatever you like.

360
00:34:41,746 --> 00:34:43,623
Try to take your mind off it.

361
00:35:12,068 --> 00:35:13,319
Going for a walk?

362
00:35:22,036 --> 00:35:23,162
Let me join you.

363
00:35:28,835 --> 00:35:30,086
Oh, right.

364
00:35:30,837 --> 00:35:33,256
Did you talk with that handsome psychic

365
00:35:33,798 --> 00:35:34,966
last night?

366
00:35:36,884 --> 00:35:39,512
Gosh, you refused to see him, didn't you?

367
00:35:39,595 --> 00:35:41,931
I told you I was quitting my job.

368
00:35:42,557 --> 00:35:44,559
What's there to talk about with a psychic?

369
00:35:45,893 --> 00:35:48,855
Don't push away someone who likes you.

370
00:35:50,231 --> 00:35:51,649
It's not like that.

371
00:35:52,608 --> 00:35:54,861
What do you mean?
I didn't mean anything romantic.

372
00:35:54,944 --> 00:35:57,572
This is just a piece of life advice.

373
00:35:57,655 --> 00:36:01,367
If you keep pushing people away,
you'll eventually be all alone.

374
00:36:03,828 --> 00:36:04,787
I don't care.

375
00:36:07,039 --> 00:36:10,918
So will you cut ties with Ms. Joo as well?

376
00:36:12,461 --> 00:36:14,881
If you live without anyone around you,

377
00:36:14,964 --> 00:36:17,466
how are you any different
from a vengeful spirit?

378
00:36:27,518 --> 00:36:29,020
I see.

379
00:36:29,103 --> 00:36:32,481
So this is the list from the employment
agency that Tae-jin gave you?

380
00:36:34,192 --> 00:36:37,486
He said he'd let me know
if Chang-hwa ever came back.

381
00:36:38,863 --> 00:36:40,281
One minute.

382
00:36:50,082 --> 00:36:51,751
ANT EMPLOYMENT AGENCY

383
00:36:55,296 --> 00:36:56,756
I found it.

384
00:37:04,263 --> 00:37:05,389
ANT EMPLOYMENT AGENCY

385
00:37:05,473 --> 00:37:07,516
I'm looking for this man.

386
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:09,435
His name is Kim Tae-jin.

387
00:37:10,561 --> 00:37:11,729
I don't know him.

388
00:37:11,812 --> 00:37:13,814
Is that so?

389
00:37:15,274 --> 00:37:16,817
All right.

390
00:37:22,198 --> 00:37:23,824
"I don't know him."

391
00:37:23,908 --> 00:37:25,576
I know you know him.

392
00:37:37,505 --> 00:37:38,923
ANT EMPLOYMENT AGENCY

393
00:37:39,006 --> 00:37:40,883
What? That's Tae-jin's minion.

394
00:37:41,926 --> 00:37:43,386
I got you.

395
00:37:47,932 --> 00:37:49,934
Someone came here looking for Tae-jin.

396
00:37:51,894 --> 00:37:52,979
-Who was it?
-Beats me.

397
00:37:53,062 --> 00:37:55,231
But I don't think Do Hak-seong sent him.

398
00:37:57,191 --> 00:37:58,276
ANT EMPLOYMENT AGENCY

399
00:38:19,547 --> 00:38:21,007
Why are you tailing me?

400
00:38:21,090 --> 00:38:23,676
-To meet Tae-jin.
-What for?

401
00:38:23,759 --> 00:38:25,845
I want to buy the memorandum.

402
00:38:25,928 --> 00:38:27,013
What?

403
00:38:27,096 --> 00:38:28,556
Tell him, and he'll know.

404
00:38:28,639 --> 00:38:32,727
Tell him I want to buy the memorandum
for 135,720,000 won.

405
00:38:33,394 --> 00:38:34,645
-That much?
-Yes.

406
00:38:37,231 --> 00:38:38,149
Your number.

407
00:38:39,233 --> 00:38:40,067
Sorry?

408
00:38:40,151 --> 00:38:43,195
I'll call you after telling him,
so give me your number.

409
00:38:43,279 --> 00:38:44,363
Yes, sir.

410
00:38:44,447 --> 00:38:46,073
BANKBOOK

411
00:38:48,284 --> 00:38:50,036
It may not have been a townhouse,

412
00:38:51,078 --> 00:38:53,622
but I wanted to get her an apartment.

413
00:38:55,791 --> 00:38:56,834
Fine.

414
00:38:57,501 --> 00:38:59,295
I can always make more money.

415
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:01,505
I should do it for In-beom.

416
00:39:03,257 --> 00:39:04,300
Mom.

417
00:39:04,967 --> 00:39:06,010
I'm sorry.

418
00:39:10,181 --> 00:39:11,223
In-beom.

419
00:39:23,778 --> 00:39:24,987
What about Ms. Hong?

420
00:39:25,071 --> 00:39:26,697
Did she not come with you?

421
00:39:34,622 --> 00:39:35,748
I understand.

422
00:39:36,791 --> 00:39:38,000
Every time she sees me,

423
00:39:39,585 --> 00:39:43,130
she'll be reminded of the painful past
that she desperately wanted to forget.

424
00:39:46,467 --> 00:39:48,052
The only thing I can do for her

425
00:39:50,221 --> 00:39:52,390
is to get out of her sight.

426
00:39:54,433 --> 00:39:55,684
What should we do?

427
00:40:02,525 --> 00:40:03,984
I resent my uncle.

428
00:40:04,944 --> 00:40:09,156
He shouldn't have set the houses on fire.
He shouldn't have taken those lives.

429
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:10,491
Don't do that.

430
00:40:11,951 --> 00:40:14,036
Do Hak-seong is to blame here.

431
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:17,623
If it wasn't for him, do you think
your uncle would've done such a thing?

432
00:40:22,586 --> 00:40:25,923
In-beom, let's get that memorandum back

433
00:40:26,882 --> 00:40:28,509
and punish that son of a gun.

434
00:40:30,052 --> 00:40:31,178
I think I will soon.

435
00:40:33,848 --> 00:40:36,225
Did Kim Tae-jin call you?

436
00:40:36,892 --> 00:40:38,352
No, but…

437
00:40:39,854 --> 00:40:41,147
I'll tell you once I'm sure.

438
00:40:43,649 --> 00:40:44,567
You trust me, right?

439
00:40:47,611 --> 00:40:48,696
DAEBAK REALTY

440
00:40:57,037 --> 00:40:58,456
Hurry up.

441
00:40:58,539 --> 00:40:59,957
-Hey, go over there.
-Yes, sir.

442
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:01,083
-You, over there.
-Yes, sir.

443
00:41:01,167 --> 00:41:02,209
-Make sure they stamp it.
-Yes, sir.

444
00:41:02,293 --> 00:41:03,836
WE'RE AGAINST THE REDEVELOPMENT
THAT WILL ROB US!

445
00:41:07,423 --> 00:41:09,091
Hello.

446
00:41:16,223 --> 00:41:17,850
REAL ESTATE PURCHASE AGREEMENT

447
00:41:23,522 --> 00:41:24,648
REAL ESTATE PURCHASE AGREEMENT

448
00:41:27,109 --> 00:41:28,152
Done.

449
00:41:41,790 --> 00:41:42,958
Honey.

450
00:41:44,627 --> 00:41:45,794
Let's…

451
00:41:48,005 --> 00:41:49,673
just sell this place and leave.

452
00:41:53,135 --> 00:41:54,428
Just give up.

453
00:41:54,512 --> 00:41:56,388
He would've come already if he wanted to.

454
00:41:56,972 --> 00:41:59,683
It's not that he can't.
He doesn't want to come back.

455
00:41:59,767 --> 00:42:01,018
If you want to leave,

456
00:42:01,685 --> 00:42:02,895
go without me.

457
00:42:03,854 --> 00:42:05,940
I'll keep waiting for our son here.

458
00:42:08,609 --> 00:42:11,362
Even if I turn into a ghost,

459
00:42:11,445 --> 00:42:14,323
I'll wait right here until he returns!

460
00:42:24,041 --> 00:42:28,796
DAEBAK REALTY

461
00:42:33,467 --> 00:42:37,263
CHANGHWA RESTAURANT

462
00:42:46,272 --> 00:42:48,107
Gosh. Those jerks.

463
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:50,150
They even cut off the electricity?

464
00:43:02,663 --> 00:43:04,790
Who… Who are you?

465
00:43:07,835 --> 00:43:08,961
Are you…

466
00:43:10,421 --> 00:43:11,255
Chang-hwa?

467
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:15,551
You're Chang-hwa, right?

468
00:43:20,306 --> 00:43:21,348
You brat.

469
00:43:21,432 --> 00:43:24,935
Where have you been all this time?
What took you so long?

470
00:43:25,019 --> 00:43:27,021
I have never been able

471
00:43:27,104 --> 00:43:29,356
to sleep soundly because of you, brat.

472
00:43:32,359 --> 00:43:33,193
What…

473
00:43:35,029 --> 00:43:36,530
What happened to your leg?

474
00:43:37,948 --> 00:43:40,200
I heard you work at a construction site.

475
00:43:41,201 --> 00:43:42,328
Did you hurt it there?

476
00:43:47,833 --> 00:43:50,544
And why do you look so messy?

477
00:43:54,632 --> 00:43:55,716
Did you eat?

478
00:43:59,094 --> 00:44:00,804
Why not?

479
00:44:01,430 --> 00:44:03,265
You can't even feed yourself?

480
00:44:05,017 --> 00:44:06,477
Wait here.

481
00:44:08,270 --> 00:44:10,856
I have kimchi stew, your favorite.

482
00:44:11,398 --> 00:44:12,566
It won't take long.

483
00:44:23,202 --> 00:44:26,121
Yes, this is Changhwa Restaurant.

484
00:44:26,205 --> 00:44:27,748
Are you Yang Chang-hwa's family?

485
00:44:27,831 --> 00:44:28,874
Yes.

486
00:44:33,962 --> 00:44:37,049
What do you mean, Chang-hwa is dead?

487
00:44:50,646 --> 00:44:53,148
Are you sure it's Chang-hwa?

488
00:44:53,232 --> 00:44:56,693
Yes. This was found in his pocket,

489
00:44:56,777 --> 00:44:59,279
so we called the number. Take a look.

490
00:45:16,839 --> 00:45:18,173
Chang-hwa.

491
00:45:18,715 --> 00:45:22,386
Chang-hwa! No, my boy…

492
00:45:22,970 --> 00:45:24,763
No.

493
00:45:27,349 --> 00:45:30,102
Chang-hwa… My boy…

494
00:45:30,853 --> 00:45:34,022
My boy, Chang-hwa.

495
00:45:35,190 --> 00:45:37,109
BLUE SALT

496
00:45:44,616 --> 00:45:45,576
Are you going home?

497
00:45:46,785 --> 00:45:49,079
I told you. I'm going to travel now.

498
00:45:51,498 --> 00:45:54,293
Sure. Enjoy your trip then.

499
00:45:54,376 --> 00:45:56,462
Come back and tell me about your trip.

500
00:45:58,046 --> 00:45:59,423
Thank you for everything.

501
00:46:04,887 --> 00:46:06,138
MS. JOO

502
00:46:06,889 --> 00:46:09,475
Yes, Ms. Joo. It's been a while.

503
00:46:10,767 --> 00:46:12,060
Who died?

504
00:46:14,229 --> 00:46:15,772
Yang Chang-hwa?

505
00:46:19,693 --> 00:46:22,696
FUNERAL HALL

506
00:46:45,928 --> 00:46:50,307
My. You must be in mourning too.
Thank you for coming.

507
00:46:51,266 --> 00:46:53,810
Gosh. Whenever you were at my restaurant,

508
00:46:53,894 --> 00:46:55,771
you always reminded me of my son.

509
00:46:56,313 --> 00:46:57,523
Goodness.

510
00:46:59,983 --> 00:47:03,362
Gosh. Hang in there.

511
00:47:08,992 --> 00:47:10,077
Ms. Hong.

512
00:47:13,747 --> 00:47:14,998
When did you get…

513
00:47:21,838 --> 00:47:23,006
Where are you going?

514
00:47:23,090 --> 00:47:27,010
Stay here a bit longer. Ms. Hong
will be uncomfortable if I'm here.

515
00:47:30,472 --> 00:47:31,723
Gosh.

516
00:48:23,025 --> 00:48:24,109
I'm sorry.

517
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:26,653
I truly thought

518
00:48:27,362 --> 00:48:29,823
what I did was best for you.

519
00:48:31,533 --> 00:48:33,327
But I was arrogant.

520
00:48:34,786 --> 00:48:36,079
Don't bother.

521
00:48:36,955 --> 00:48:38,999
I'm not asking for your forgiveness.

522
00:48:39,082 --> 00:48:41,209
But if you are

523
00:48:41,710 --> 00:48:44,129
blaming yourself for this,

524
00:48:46,673 --> 00:48:48,425
I don't want you to do that.

525
00:48:50,385 --> 00:48:52,179
That's what I wanted to tell you.

526
00:48:56,558 --> 00:48:57,476
I'll leave now.

527
00:49:13,075 --> 00:49:14,076
DAEBAK REALTY

528
00:49:34,638 --> 00:49:36,139
DAEBAK REALTY

