00:51:17,991 --> 00:51:19,576
CHANGHWA RESTAURANT

532
00:51:52,734 --> 00:51:54,236
Money, money. Stop saying that!

533
00:51:54,736 --> 00:51:56,696
Fine. I'll go out and make money.

534
00:51:56,780 --> 00:51:58,240
Gosh. As if.

535
00:52:06,957 --> 00:52:08,458
Why did I

536
00:52:09,251 --> 00:52:11,545
have to be so mean to him?

537
00:52:20,470 --> 00:52:22,264
Chang-hwa.

538
00:52:28,812 --> 00:52:30,188
Chang-hwa…

539
00:53:01,887 --> 00:53:03,138
Ms. Hong.

540
00:53:03,972 --> 00:53:05,807
Are you in?

541
00:53:15,692 --> 00:53:18,987
Thanks a lot for coming to the funeral.

542
00:53:19,571 --> 00:53:21,865
I haven't been in my right mind,

543
00:53:22,490 --> 00:53:23,992
so I forgot to thank you.

544
00:53:25,368 --> 00:53:27,037
Of course, I should go.

545
00:53:38,673 --> 00:53:39,841
Listen.

546
00:53:41,593 --> 00:53:42,802
I…

547
00:53:46,389 --> 00:53:49,643
I don't know if I've gone insane.

548
00:53:50,477 --> 00:53:51,645
But I…

549
00:53:54,356 --> 00:53:56,274
I keep seeing my dead son.

550
00:53:59,444 --> 00:54:03,573
I must be seeing things, right?

551
00:54:07,202 --> 00:54:08,787
He didn't become a ghost, did he?

552
00:54:15,961 --> 00:54:17,170
That darned rascal.

553
00:54:19,047 --> 00:54:20,715
Why didn't he come sooner?

554
00:54:23,343 --> 00:54:25,595
He couldn't even die in peace.

555
00:54:28,390 --> 00:54:29,683
I feel so bad for him.

556
00:54:33,895 --> 00:54:36,898
My poor son.

557
00:54:42,404 --> 00:54:44,072
Ms. Hong.

558
00:54:44,698 --> 00:54:46,866
Could you help my son leave in peace?

559
00:54:46,950 --> 00:54:50,120
Please, I ask of you.

560
00:54:51,121 --> 00:54:53,331
Please do that for my poor Chang-hwa.

561
00:55:46,551 --> 00:55:48,636
YANG CHANG-HWA

562
00:55:59,397 --> 00:56:03,651
She'll suffer longer if I waste time
looking for another psychic,

563
00:56:03,735 --> 00:56:05,487
so I called you to do this quickly.

564
00:56:07,322 --> 00:56:09,365
Thanks for calling me.

565
00:56:31,513 --> 00:56:32,722
Let's go.

566
00:56:32,806 --> 00:56:34,307
CHANGHWA RESTAURANT

567
00:56:38,061 --> 00:56:39,521
Did you know him well?

568
00:56:40,396 --> 00:56:41,356
Yes.

569
00:56:55,286 --> 00:56:56,621
We'll begin.

570
00:56:57,330 --> 00:56:59,207
Until it's all over,

571
00:57:00,250 --> 00:57:01,584
keep your eyes closed.

572
00:57:04,212 --> 00:57:05,213
If we do this,

573
00:57:06,131 --> 00:57:09,217
Chang-hwa will leave
this world for good, right?

574
00:57:11,845 --> 00:57:12,679
Yes.

575
00:57:49,174 --> 00:57:50,216
Take your necklace off.

576
00:58:11,821 --> 00:58:14,282
In-beom!

577
00:58:14,908 --> 00:58:16,034
In-beom!

578
00:58:21,831 --> 00:58:22,832
Are you okay?

579
00:58:26,586 --> 00:58:27,504
What happened?

580
00:58:34,594 --> 00:58:35,637
Mom.

581
00:58:40,892 --> 00:58:43,144
This is the same as what happened then.

582
00:59:04,207 --> 00:59:05,542
I…

583
00:59:07,085 --> 00:59:09,212
killed my son.

584
00:59:12,924 --> 00:59:14,801
I'm the one who killed him.

585
00:59:18,972 --> 00:59:21,432
It's not the vengeful spirit
that's refusing to leave.

586
00:59:22,850 --> 00:59:24,978
She's keeping him from leaving.

587
01:00:16,362 --> 01:00:20,283
My obsession is the reason
my mom can't leave.

588
01:00:20,366 --> 01:00:21,451
No!

589
01:00:21,534 --> 01:00:23,453
You look so unstable.
How can I leave you alone?

590
01:00:23,536 --> 01:00:26,164
Have I ever told you about my daughter?

591
01:00:26,247 --> 01:00:29,083
Before we see another one
become a vengeful spirit because of him,

592
01:00:29,167 --> 01:00:31,461
someone has to stop Do Hak-seong.

593
01:00:31,544 --> 01:00:33,838
The chairman will die of shock
once he sees this.

594
01:00:33,921 --> 01:00:35,173
I'm on my way to see the chairman.

595
01:00:35,256 --> 01:00:36,132
Where's the memorandum?

596
01:00:36,215 --> 01:00:37,342
Do you know what it means to me?

597
01:00:37,425 --> 01:00:40,303
The In-beom I know
wouldn't give up this easily.

598
01:00:40,386 --> 01:00:41,804
Everything is ready, so take your time.

599
01:00:41,888 --> 01:00:43,723
Chairman Do Hak-seong has been…

600
01:00:43,806 --> 01:00:45,350
There's a possibility of murder.

601
01:00:45,433 --> 01:00:46,267
In-beom.

